i later on went home . i remember meeting dad on my way home .
i was very sad and i asked him why my friends had laughed at me telling me i am a tutsi .
"@ what does being tutsi mean ? @"
i asked him .
he told me @: "@ i do n't know how to explain that to you ... that 's just the way things are ... @" he told me he would one day explain to me as i needed to know that i was actually tutsi .
he said he also found things that way ... when i got home , i asked mother for more explanations .
she then told me @: "@ in rwanda , there are twas , hutus and tutsis .
