well even before , people were killed but because i was running all the time , i never observed it clearly like then .
i would just run for my own life .
so , as we piped , we saw someone who was being killed with a machete . that was in nyamata town .
whenever he would try to stand up , he would be slashed then he would fall down again , he was slashed until he died .
they were playing on his mind asking him , "@ you cockroach where were you going ? @"
i was silently listening from that house .
