it was terrible .
i remember one day a boy called rushonji and i and other boys ; we were eight in total . we walked down to the swamp to hide thinking that at least we could rest from running that day . we hid in groups of two to avoid being in a big group . before we entered the swamp , we would cut banana leaves to spread them down where we would sit , but that did not stop us from getting wet . at around nine o'clock , we heard the attackers coming to the swamp . there were other interahamwe who were up on the hill to watch people who were hiding in the swamp , then they would shout directing the others about which side we were hiding . within a short time they were near us . they were six interahamwe and we were two , the other boy and i , one attacker had a sharp metal , others had machetes and another one had a club .
they asked us " what are you doing in this swamp ? @"
we said , "@ nothing . @"
