they found 80.000 frw .
they were amazed .
they almost fought over the money but their leader stopped them and took the money and said , "@ i know he has some more . @"
they searched in ( mugondo ) the short he was wearing beneath his trousers and got 5,000 francs then they started discussing among themselves what was going to be the next step .
some would say , "@ let us clear them off @" others would say , "@ we have taken a lot of money from them .
