someone did not see what took place during the genocide , for example the people who came from the neighbouring countries and who did not see what happened besides hearing it from people .
well some of these people say that they want to join the survivors association .
some join and sometimes get traumatised after hearing people 's testimonies within the association .
that is a simple example .
but i personally if i get my own children , i will tell my children the stories of genocide and show them the consequences of it .
i will show them my scar of the 1994 genocide .
i know it will be hard .
