instead i would think about what had happened to me and i 'd suddenly feel so confused .
yes ... my mum was also shot .
she was a "@ born again christian . @" she liked praying so much ; all i would hear her say was , "@ jesus christ @"@ .
and my brothers were next to each other ; they were made to sit in a line like this ... i heard people screaming besides .
