but my sister tried to contact farg and then farg considered our problem .
and they would give us 20,000 frw per month .
then in the year 2001 , which is when we used to get the funding of farg ... my sister too ... i was in secondary five .
my sister realised that her life was also getting worse because she never had any documents [ diplomas or certificates ] .
the war began when she was in secondary two .
then she told me , "@ you have reached in senior five and you can see that farg is helping us ; they provide us with school funds , transport and other school expenses .
