my name is olivier ruyenzi , son of venuste karasira and of speciose mukakarangwa .
i was born in 1984 .
after habyarimana 's death is when ... two days later is when we went to eto school .
we found the unamir soldiers there .
we went there at around 1 p.m. when we got there , our houseboy went back home and when he got back , he told us our house had already been burnt .
we continued living at eto , many of the people from kicukiro , the neighbourhood where we lived .
people came to eto hoping that they 'd survive .
a few days later , on april 11th , 1994 is when the unamir soldiers made an announcement from the un saying that they needed to leave .
they left with all the white people and the catholic nuns who were working in a convent that was there .
