because all our neighbours had sought refuge in our home with a belief that , since it was in a white family no body would guess they were there or bather to come .
personally i thought so . therefore , i would put them in the bedrooms and under the beds .
then us , we remained in the colidor thinking that , "@ if they find us in the colidor they would n't bather to check . @" therefore , i asked him to get out , "@ if they find you outside , they will not have a chance to enter because if they enter they will search around the house . @" i explained to him .
